{"tid":1398978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"民主的秘技 公開扯貓尾","createTime":"2019-08-03T04:08:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T09:21:20.000Z","uid":107060,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"55c64fa10a155758c18724d0cca649256c49797c","tid":1398978,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T04:08:40.000Z","msg":"民主的秘技 公開扯貓尾<br />\nSource:<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/pseudobiologist/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fpseudobiologist%2F&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDfPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=2e209be8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/pseudobiologist/</a><br />\n<br />\n特朗普早前在香港的問題上有點軟化，一方面吩咐美國官員不要胡亂評論香港事務，另一方面又稱香港的示威為騷亂（Riots），更稱香港與中共的事務，要自己解決。<br />\n<br />\n事隔不足一日，美國國會議員魯比奧（Rubio），就要求總統特朗普譴責中共國破壞香港自治。文中，更稱香港為「香港特別自治區」（Hong Kong Special Autonomous Region）。而的確，香港自治的重要性極高，是國家主權的體現。<br />\n<br />\n為何特朗普和魯比奧會對香港分別發出兩個不同的意見？這正是民主政府的好處，虛實難測。<br />\n<br />\n不過，其實再看前一日中共國外交部的發言，竟要求美國勸喻香港的示威者，就能再看清楚一點。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普的發言其實是指：「你中共國廢物，搞不好香港就來怪老子我？還叫我幫忙！我聽了你的話，豈不是公開承認老子搞亂你？你自己做錯事，後果自負。」然後，魯比奧要求譴責中共國破壞香港自治。結合起來，就是&mdash;&mdash;因為中共國破壞香港自治，導致香港出現騷亂。<br />\n<br />\n這個回應，中共外交部又呆了。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普的發言<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/amp/s/mobile.reuters.com/article/amp/idUSKCN1US0OR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Famp%2Fs%2Fmobile.reuters.com%2Farticle%2Famp%2FidUSKCN1US0OR&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDfPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=0ae762f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/amp/s/mobile.reuters.com/article/amp/idUSKCN1US0OR</a><br />\n<br />\n議員 Rubio 的發言<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rubio.senate.gov/public/index.cfm/2019/8/rubio-colleagues-urge-president-trump-to-condemn-china-s-efforts-to-undermine-hong-kong-s-autonomy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rubio.senate.gov%2Fpublic%2Findex.cfm%2F2019%2F8%2Frubio-colleagues-urge-president-trump-to-condemn-china-s-efforts-to-undermine-hong-kong-s-autonomy&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDfPwW8VRzHVpxLRgBu58%2FEQ%3D&h=e91bff85\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rubio.senate.gov/public/index.cfm/2019/8/rubio-colleagues-urge-president-trump-to-condemn-china-s-efforts-to-undermine-hong-kong-s-autonomy</a>"},{"pid":"867470b4f4354c1a23c52e8930895dd9dad64a6e","tid":1398978,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4184645ba169a7afa89b1b453427daab77e80ae","tid":1398978,"uid":64938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:44:10.000Z","msg":"[香城online]傳令兵的技巧和心得<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382782\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382782</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n就快又發夢啦，手足幫手廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8d6743cb19bedb8bfeb1a3aa137aa8e444a3d74","tid":1398978,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T09:21:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}